name: The gaze of the fairies
description:
Juliette is a seven years old girl, fascinated by the world and with the innate curiosity of children.

This photograph represents his infinite gaze, which he can enclose from pieces of rainbows,

even the colors of the jungle and the sea.

A simple look but one that can naturally express all the force of life.

Thanks for collaborating with @Cyndidreamer (ig). All proceeds from the NFTs will be used to continue creating art with Juliette.
